translations: 随意翻阅（paginate 的过去式和过去分词）

sentences.sentence: Occurs when all document content has been paginated.
sentences.translation: 所有的文件内容都已分页时发生。

sentences.sentence: On some devices, the list will be paginated. Set the.
sentences.translation: 在一些设备上，必须对列表进行分页。

sentences.sentence: Occurs when one or more content pages have been paginated.
sentences.translation: 当一个或多个内容页面已分页时发生。
